channel.title: Can't log in on server
channel.description: Hello, I just created a server and me and my friend started programming on it, everything worked fine untill this message appeared when we tryed to log in. [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/fnensw.png[/img] Can you please help us? Wartek

item.title: Can't log in on server

item.description:

[quote=“I r Pwn u, post:6, topic:446836”][quote author=wartek link=topic=549717.msg4029511#msg4029511 date=1340625930]

That’s why you should [quote author=wartek link=topic=549717.msg4029497#msg4029497 date=1340623093]

Hmm never seen that error before. What was the last update you did before this error?

I think I added a command “mod island”.
But I guess I accidently deleted something and now it doesn’t work.
Edit:I’m using delta:)
